<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="curtain-n">curtain <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɜːtn/    美 /'kɜːrtn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>帘；窗帘；门帘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please <strong>draw the curtains</strong>; the sunlight is too bright.
请拉上窗帘，阳光太强了。</p><footer>人教① – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(剧院的) 幕；帷幕：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As <strong>the curtain rises</strong>, a cottage is seen on the stage.
幕布升起时，舞台上出现了一所农舍。</p></div></div>